   Pet Furniture July 3, 2017
   Comments (0) Cat House

TARDIS Cat Houses

   If you are a cat person and a sci-fi nerd, you’ll appreciate this novel
   idea: a Doctor Who and Star Wars inspired cat houses. Bulgaria-based
   design studio CacaoPets creates these and other cool designs from 100%
   recyclable cardboard. The houses are light, foldable, and will look
   charming in any sci-fi-loving home. Other themes and designs include
   Taj Mahal, war tank, castle tower, just to name a few. Available for
   purchase here.

   Via

